dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jason Jones. May I have your name please?
Hi, my name is Amber Ross.
Nice to meet you, Amber! Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, my policy number is five one two three four.
Thank you, Amber. Can you confirm your date of birth for verification purposes?
My date of birth is zero five dash one four dash one nine eight seven.
Great, thank you for confirming. Is there anything specific you need assistance with today?
I wanted to check the status of a claim I filed last week.
I can assist you with that. Thank you for your patience, Amber. I will look into your claim status.
Thank you for contacting us today, Amber. Have a great day!
